<p style="text-align: left;">I was at a bar recently talking with a friend about how excited we both were for this book. Granted I am usually talking about books, but still! R.F. Kuang is one of the best fantasy authors working right now and Iâ€™m truly so stoked about this book. <em>Katabasis</em> is about a graduate student at the Cambridge school of Magick who has to team up with her rival to journey into Hell and save the soul of her favorite professor. I donâ€™t know what more I can say. If that description doesnâ€™t immediately launch this book to the top of your TBR, we could never be friends.Â <em>â€“McKayla Coyle, <a href="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-most-anticipated-books-of-2025-part-two/">as recommended in our second-half of 2025 list</a></em></p>
