<p>New Ken Liu!! New Ken Liu!! On the heels of his recent translation of the Dao De Jing, Liu returns to original speculative fiction with this series opener that follows a famous â€œorphan hackerâ€ as she tries to help save a kidnapped â€˜dream artistâ€™ who can manipulate shared virtual landscapes. It sounds like a great technothriller and Liu, one of our great speculative minds, is a sure-fire bet for a good time.Â <em>â€“DB, <a href="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-most-anticipated-books-of-2025-part-two/">as recommended in our second-half of 2025 list</a></em></p>
